## Customize flags given to the VM: https://www.erlang.org/doc/man/erl.html
## -mode/-name/-sname/-setcookie are configured via env vars, do not set them here.

## Ignore the emulator break signal so Ctrl+C cannot open the BREAK menu
## and bypass OTP shutdown with the interactive "abort" action. Product
## wrappers translate INT/TERM into SIGTERM for a normal OTP shutdown path.
+B i
